page.title: 15Housing in our 'D' block
page.content: There are lots of different houses in our area. In{Chalfont Common}there are many houses.The houses are by the lanes. They are situated in a fairly quiet place.The gardens are nicely kept and well set out.Some of the houses in {Chalfont Common}are bungalows. Bungalows are one storey houses so the bedrooms and are on the same floor as the lounge and kitchen.There are shops in{Chalfont Common}too.The shops are mainly food shops. In{Maple Cross}there are all sorts of houses there are detached,semi detached,bungalows and flats.The houses along Chalfont Road are semi detached.The people live in flats have got commual gardens.In some flats when you speak you hear your echo.There are very few bungalows in{Maple Cross;} there are a few along Denham Way.
